OL,3,CElderly woman found lying in road
OL,4,Cafter hit and run
OL,6,FA 'seriously injured' elderly woman
OL,7,Fwas found lying in the road after
OL,8,Fbeing struck down by a "large vehicle"
OL,9,Fin a hit-and-run in Bolton.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,Fscene on Moss Bank Way, close to the
OL,13,Fjunction of Hillview Road, after the
OL,14,F89-year-old woman was found in the
OL,15,Froad at around 10.10am on Saturday 15
OL,16,FJune.
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police said the
OL,19,Fwoman suffered "serious injuries".
