OL,3,CElderly woman found lying in road
OL,4,Cafter hit and run
OL,6,FShe was taken to hospital from the
OL,7,Fscene and remains there in a stable
OL,8,Fcondition with wrist and knee
OL,9,Ffractures.
OL,11,FPolice believe the woman was knocked
OL,12,Fto the floor after being struck by a
OL,13,Fsilver or grey SUV-type vehicle.
OL,15,FShe was crossing the road when the
OL,16,Fvehicle hit her and fled the scene.
OL,18,FOfficers believe the driver had turned
OL,19,Fleft out of Hillview Road and onto
OL,20,FMoss Bank Way when the vehicle hit the
OL,21,Fvictim.
