OL,6,FThe driver then headed westbound onto
OL,7,Fthe main road and towards the
OL,8,Fdirection of Moss Bank Park.
OL,10,FIn an appeal issued on Sunday 16 June,
OL,11,Fpolice urged the driver to hand
OL,12,Fthemselves in.
OL,14,FAn investigation into the incident
OL,15,Fremains underway with officers
OL,16,Freviewing CCTV footage in the area.
OL,18,FAny witnesses, or any drivers with
OL,19,Fdash cam footage, are also being
OL,20,Fencouraged to come forward.
