OL,3,CElderly woman found lying in road
OL,4,Cafter hit and run
OL,6,FChief Inspector Michael Parker from
OL,7,FGMP's Roads Policing Unit said: "We
OL,8,Fare investigating a road traffic
OL,9,Fcollision, where a large vehicle
OL,10,Fstruck an elderly woman, while she was
OL,11,Fcrossing the road near the shops in
OL,12,FAstley Bridge.
OL,14,F"The scene has now been stood down
OL,15,Fwhile officers review CCTV footage and
OL,16,Fcontinue to speak with people who were
OL,17,Fin the area at the time of this
OL,18,Fincident, aiming to identify the
OL,19,Fdriver of the vehicle who failed to
OL,20,Fstop.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
