OL,6,F"We urge the driver to come forward
OL,7,Fand if you have any information,
OL,8,Fdashcam or mobile phone footage that
OL,9,Fcould support our investigation,
OL,10,Fplease call 101 quoting log 1049 of 15
OL,11,FJune 2024.
OL,13,F"Information can also be shared using
OL,14,Four LiveChat function on our website:
OL,15,Fwww.gmp.police.uk or via 101. In an
OL,16,Femergency, always dial 999.
OL,17,FAlternatively, you can contact the
OL,18,Findependent charity - Crimestoppers -
OL,19,Fanonymously on 0800 555 111."
